%
Thinking doesn't guarantee that you won't make mistakes. Not thinking
guarantees that you will.[38;5;8m - Leslie Lamport[0m
%
The right way to think about distributed systems, and I've been doing it for 40
years, is in terms of the state of the system.[38;5;8m - Leslie Lamport[0m
%
To the extent that [Agile software development] is [an excuse for not
