Musk's 1st rule of manufacturing: Make requirements less dumb. Document who is
responsible for the requirement or constraint, why it exists, and how to
contact them.
%
Musk's 2nd rule of manufacturing: Delete the part or process. If you're not
occasionally adding things back in, you're not deleting enough.
%
Musk's 3rd rule of manufacturing: Simplify or optimize. But do not optimize
things that should not exist.
%
Musk's 4th rule of manufacturing: Accelerate cycle times. You're moving too
slowly, go faster. But if you're digging your grave, don't dig it faster.
%
Musk's 5th rule of manufacturing: Automate. But never do this first.
